column3: Why do you waste your time, Bob?
She broke your heart before, she'll do it again.
I'm not talking about the princess, Kobbler. I'm here for the orb!
Bravo Bob! You're finally using your head.
Too bad you're gonna lose it!
Looks like your burnt your Kobbler.
Is it true, Bob? You didn't come for me? You came for... this?
No worries! Now killing you is a whole lot easier.
